{"tid":1846891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（最強文宣）連濃牆寫遺信有無得諗","createTime":"2020-01-27T18:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T14:17:17.000Z","uid":72431,"like":85,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"969b08030ca301ce30cc8031ee8ba370c0b7e7e1","tid":1846891,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:52:54.000Z","msg":"又唔封關<br />\n遲早都要死<br />\n<br />\n手寫又好<br />\n電腦打又好<br />\n<br />\n加兩滴血甚佳"},{"pid":"184c4c86f7d1dffcc195ce422a89b28be52f0953","tid":1846891,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:54:10.000Z","msg":"我希望大家同我一齊嗌!! 嗌到大陸都一齊嗌!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846888</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>抗疫保命<br />\n推翻政權</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54bcbb7cf36a9670271d2ed51e5ff02cb379b7d8","tid":1846891,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:55:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1dd755e6990613ae47d457c91343bd02e975a090","tid":1846891,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:56:07.000Z","msg":"Jeng"},{"pid":"7ff16eeda06b816ffbb78b9b66131a6bfc3b11e1","tid":1846891,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:56:52.000Z","msg":"記唔記得大家細個點解驚法輪功<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得貼 支那人啲 cls言論 好過 冇啦啦貼遺信"},{"pid":"8f8eb4e6d76f43bee0eb74f51a9298ddce31eb55","tid":1846891,"uid":285243,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:06:02.000Z","msg":"唔好<br />\n會狼來了"},{"pid":"ad4590dcbd117566fdf0a1045183c60201920e19","tid":1846891,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:20:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25c399214f9264af749151b262c89606099e0adf","tid":1846891,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:47:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd02d764b995185798536adcd5c65e75f12bf973","tid":1846891,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:53:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f7b83ab77543a7768a65d8d61a59c4601ecbc9c","tid":1846891,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:58:07.000Z","msg":"岩就幫手推上熱門"},{"pid":"750ac898c96b7748b0efec6b50e0cc4a656f1bbf","tid":1846891,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T20:01:4